  <h2>Outcome</h2>
  <p>The side‑pane framework created through this work went on to be reused across multiple Copilot AI upsell projects, extending its impact beyond the initial experiment. Through the process, I strengthened my growth design practice—deepening my experience with personalization, data‑informed decision‑making, and shipping within a legacy product. While the original experiment was later sunsetted, the work sharpened my growth design practice and reinforced a core belief: effective growth comes from showing value at the right moment, not forcing an upgrade.</p>
